fields.label: Resources Page
fields.content:
RESOURCES

Page 1

This is a 2-page worksheet.

Page 1 is the "RESOURCES" page.
Enter companies by order of arrival on this page.

Page 2 is the "ASSIGNMENTS" page.
This page shows companies assigned to each group. The assignments on this page are populated from page 1. Any assignment on this page can be edited at any time.

NOTE: Any company changes made on page 2 will NOT change information on page 1.
